3. Vertex-correction parameters  (data/Vz/vz_corrector_params.txt)
------------------------------------------------------------------

Per-cell vertex-correction coefficients for the CLAS12 RG-D solid targets,
copied verbatim from the clas-framework analysis repository. CLAS12
collaboration product.


4. Cut values and parameter tables  (config/cuts.json, src/selection/)
----------------------------------------------------------------------

The electron sampling-fraction polynomials, vertex windows, fiducial cuts and
DIS cuts are CLAS12 RG-D analysis parameters, transcribed from the
clas-framework analysis repository. They are physics constants of the
experiment rather than original software.


